Package: xwait
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: wait for emerging X window
 xwait waits for creation of any X window and optionally starts a command
 after setting up the event filter. This can be useful for startup of X
 sessions with some window managers.
